cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NA 

The paper deals with multi-dimensional data classification, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method is specifically designed for tensor data, which is a common data structure in multimedia analysis (cs.MM) and numerical analysis (cs.NA).
